Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:23.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How long do you plan on sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:25.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}School is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:30.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's going on? I'm sure there are better ways to wake someone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:32.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:35.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I need your advice on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that how you ask for someone's help?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:39.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't mind the details, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:42.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll see this is a great bargain for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:46.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with the skeptical look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:48.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright, I'll hear out whatever story you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:51.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}First of all, I'd like you to go up to the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do I have to follow you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you hatching?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:03.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... I think you're from next door's class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh, Sanae... I don't think I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no, I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:17.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're Elen's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fujiwara-san, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Fujieda... I'm Fujieda Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You also know Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:26.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:30.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We used to be classmates in our first year of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, did you want something with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, you see, I want to ask you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does it have something to do with Elen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:47.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to ask about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-san, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you have someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:59.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure it wouldn't be someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:03.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So basically... eh... ah... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:10.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Brother, what are you doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:12.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...in this kind of place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder who you're talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you know Mio, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:20.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, um, by the way, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was looking for Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I suddenly wanted to eat waffles at Kanekoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just wondering if Mio wanted to come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:32.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have business to take care of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:34.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did I disturb you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She confessed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:45.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:47.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fujiwara-san was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Fujieda. But, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio confessed to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio has weird tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And then, how did you reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I couldn't because you barged in and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:04.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio would want to hear the answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's me who was disturbing you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't let her leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:15.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But what should I tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to think about that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though I set up a meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...why can't you two make any progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:35.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should have done like we practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"I love you, please be my boyfriend!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:45.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say that, and watch him as he's forced to nod.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Time taken, 5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A confession is like a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What made you drag it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:56.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:00.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh damn it, this is our last spring of school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you want to waste this chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Awesome timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just about to go look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A good thing you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:11.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have something to talk about with Fujieda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Make yourself scarce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:13.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:22.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In that case I'll grant your wish and get out of here, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What were you doing, Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:28.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:32.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fujieda-san, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The answer to back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was all a bit sudden, so I didn't know what do say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't eavesdrop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, what did you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told her we could start off by being friends for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a commonplace answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's your sense of style?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:00.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So... did you set up arrangements with your "friend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll head out to town together tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:07.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Escort her well, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:16.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And if you do something embarrassing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:18.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A bit violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll cheer you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio is a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, from our little chat I felt so already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, give me a special allowance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I already gave you this month's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:31.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:39.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You already agreed on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's a big step for a late bloomer like Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What were you all talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, hey. Thanks for having me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:49.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huge scandal! There's big news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tomorrow, Mio will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:58.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:00.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, you have a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you have the lunch box?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Check! Well then, I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:09.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright, with this your grade is 40 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a low score.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you remember what I taught you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you a host or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Originally I wanted to invite you to a restaurant, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You live with Elen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Both our parents died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:07.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It happened when I was young. I'm over it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I live with only my mother too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:19.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But when I see her being so busy with work...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:23.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If only my father were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's what I think then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:27.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to support her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When you need a man to do something, call me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks, I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mm, next thing up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that Sanae's handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Go to a place you shouldn't mention."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's the place you shouldn't mention?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You finally step up the ladder of adulthood like Cinderella did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:58.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you finish it according to the plan, today's date will be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sanae that little broad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A woman is riding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:18.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's incredible how she can handle such a huge motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:21.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Riding such an expensive bike is impossible for a beggar like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh, when did it fall down?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji...-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The silencer concealed most of the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe a 9mm parabellum round?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've woken...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...from my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:36.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I went from Mexico to Peru and from there to the Philippines via Palau,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and came to Japan half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:46.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}to this city, trying to forget the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:03.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After you returned to this country, you really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know by looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are opening up your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:13.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's probably only natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:14.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...in your homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is as far as it gets, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're coming after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:21.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Inferno?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I got a silent warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So it is time for us to wake from the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If at all possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I had wanted you to remain fast asleep in this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forgetting about your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:40.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I still need to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who are you repenting to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To God Himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someday I will meet Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Inferno is coming for us at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to do this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will use Fujieda-san's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fujieda-san's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:10.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Right after she was born, Fujieda-san's parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:20.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I heard that from her as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Her father went missing and was never found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:25.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She grew up being told that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She still believes that lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Her father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...is worth being written of in newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Godou Kaiten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's the leader of a large-scale yakuza group, the Godou clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:41.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Godou clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fujieda was brought up by her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, the Godou clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About that, does she...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:54.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:14:02.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even within the clan, only a handful of people know of Mio's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:07.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Godou Kaiten hid his wife and their daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...in order to protect them from his enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then Mio is Godou Daisuke's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're siblings from different mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:22.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Godou Kaiten won't let his daughter get caught up in his organization's battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but he can't protect her out in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:30.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mio is Godou Kaiten's biggest weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where did you get that information?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard it from Scythe Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:41.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After he fled from Inferno,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he hid himself in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you that before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:47.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:52.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At that time, Master investigated the Godou clan thouroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:58.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He planned to exploit Kaiten's only weakness for his own ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:14:59.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:03.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen, don't tell me you plan to use Fujieda-san to threaten the Godou clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At the right time, she could be an trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:11.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The young leader who stands at the top of the Godou clan, Shiga Toru,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:14.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}is loyal to Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you understand the situation now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:28.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if it's Inferno that stands in your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you hold Mio captive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why didn't you tell me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I should have told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:41.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I knew Mio had feelings for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:44.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I would have told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I had known they would come after us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the end our normal life didn't last very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have to make arrangements for our escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:31.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We need to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:33.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In these times, you can cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now you can be like in the days of old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:46.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That would be selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm prepared for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We are being chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:56.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, you've forgotten something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But maybe that's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:02.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...was happy because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:04.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For the last half a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}your smile and your sleeping face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...showed true happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By watching them alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This thing called homeland...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...puts you at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someday, I too will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I can keep on living a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:39.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...that someday you would find my homeland as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:51.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want your happiness until now to have been a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someday, we can come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:59.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if we go abroad, this country will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:04.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure the day will come when you can return here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:09.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The day when we can truly live a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That time just hasn't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:27.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:31.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji went home in the middle of a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It wasn't a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:36.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Reiji-san said he had urgent business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For young people in the full bloom of their youth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there's nothing more important than love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:44.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're a bit loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:48.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though I went to the trouble of setting up a plan for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maybe that was a bit unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a pity the date went bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:53.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, "I guess so"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speak of the devil,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sa-Sanae?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sanae, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:37.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-san, yesterday was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did your urgent business go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yup, it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:47.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're pretty good to block my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You get second place after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:51.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have some business with Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:58.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! Where are you going leaving your girlfriend behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, did I upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something is different about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:08.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's not his usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:20.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:22.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:32.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No... is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:37.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice to meet you, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:44.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or should I call you "ex-Phantom"?
